quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,Twaa-Siin; iyo ni imirongo ya Qur’an ikaba n’igitabo gisobanutse (kinashyira ibintu ku mugaragaro)
  27,2,(Iyo mirongo) ni umuyoboro ndetse ikaba n’inkuru nziza ku bemera
  27,3,"Ba bandi bahozaho iswala, bagatanga amaturo, kandi bakemera badashidikanya umunsi w’imperuka"
  27,4,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi batemera imperuka, twabakundishije ibikorwa byabo (ibibi bakabibonamo ibyiza), bityo bakaba barindagira"
  27,5,"Abo ni bo bazabona ibihano bibi (kuri iyi si), kandi ku munsi w’imperuka ni bo bazaba abanyagihombo gikabije"
  27,6,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, wowe (Muhamadi) wakira Qur’an iturutse kuri Nyirubugenge buhambaye (Allah), Umumenyi uhebuje"
  27,7,(Wibuke) ubwo Musa yabwiraga umuryango we (igihe yavaga i Mediyani ajya Misiri) ati “Mu by’ukuri njye ndabutswe umuriro; ndaje mbazanire amakuru yawo (yadufasha kumenya inzira) cyangwa mbazanire igishirira cyaka kugira ngo mwote.”
  27,8,"Ubwo yawugeragaho, yarahamagawe (arabwirwa) ati “Yuje umugisha uri muri uyu muriro n’abari iruhande rwawo; kandi ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose.”"
  27,9,"Yewe Musa! Mu by’ukuri ni Njye Allah, Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  27,10,"(Allah aravuga ati) “Ngaho naga inkoni yawe hasi!” Maze (Musa ayinaze) ayibona yinyagambura nk’inzoka, ahindukira yiruka ntiyagaruka inyuma. (Allah aramubwira ati) “Yewe Musa! Witinya! Mu by’ukuri iwanjye Intumwa ntizitinya.”"
  27,11,"Uretse uwakoze ikibi hanyuma ikibi (yakoze) akagisimbuza icyiza. Mu by’ukuri ndi Nyir’ukubabarira, Nyirimpuhwe"
  27,12,"Unashyire ukuboko kwawe (ikiganza cyawe) mu kwaha, uragukuramo kwererana ntacyo kwabaye. (Iki ni kimwe) mu bitangaza icyenda (wahawe ngo ubyifashishe) kwa Farawo n’abantu be. Mu by’ukuri bo ni abantu b’ibyigomeke"
  27,13,"Ariko ubwo ibitangaza byacu bisobanutse byabageragaho ku buryo bugaragara, baravuze bati “Ubu ni uburozi bugaragara.”"
  27,14,"Nuko barabihinyura bidakwiye ndetse baranibona, nyamara imitima yabo ibihamya (ko ari ukuri). Ngaho reba uko iherezo ry’abangizi ryagenze"
  27,15,"Kandi rwose twahaye ubumenyi Dawudi na Sulayimani (Salomo), maze bombi baravuga bati “Ishimwe n’ikuzo ni ibya Allah, We waturutishije benshi mu bagaragu be b’abemeramana.”"
  27,16,"Kandi Sulayimani yazunguye (ubuhanuzi, ubumenyi n’ubwami bwa) Dawudi, nuko aravuga ati “Yemwe bantu! Twigishijwe (kumva) imvugo z’inyoni kandi duhabwa buri kintu. Mu by’ukuri izi ni ingabire zigaragara (ziturutse kwa Allah).”"
  27,17,"Nuko Sulayimani akoranyirizwa ingabo ze zo mu majini no mu bantu ndetse no mu nyoni, maze zishyirwa mu masibo"
  27,18,"Kugeza ubwo bageraga mu kibaya cy’inshishi, rumwe mu nshishi rukavuga ruti “Mwa nshishi mwe! Nimwinjire mu buturo bwanyu, Sulayimani n’ingabo ze batabasyonyora batabizi.”"
  27,19,"Nuko (Sulayimani) aramwenyura asetswa n’iryo jambo ryarwo, maze aravuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Nshoboza gushimira inema zawe wampundagajeho, njye n’ababyeyi banjye, unanshoboze gukora ibitunganye wishimira. Kandi unanyinjize mu bagaragu bawe beza ku bw’impuhwe zawe.”"
  27,20,Nuko agenzura inyoni maze aravuga ati “Ko ntabona Samusure (Hud Hud)? Cyangwa iri mu zidahari
  27,21,"Mu by’ukuri ndayihanisha igihano gikaze cyangwa nyibage, cyeretse ninzanira impamvu zumvikana.”"
  27,22,"Nuko bidatinze (Samusure) iraza maze iravuga iti “Namenye ibyo utamenye kandi nje nturutse i Saba-i (Sheba muri Yemen), nkuzaniye inkuru y’impamo.”"
  27,23,"Mu by’ukuri nahasanze umugore (witwa Balqis ari we) ubategeka. Kandi yahawe buri kintu, ndetse afite n’intebe y’ubwami ihambaye"
  27,24,"Nasanze we n’abantu be bubamira izuba mu cyimbo cya Allah. Kandi Shitani yabakundishije ibikorwa byabo (bibi), inabakumira kugana inzira (igororotse), bityo ntibayoboka"
  27,25,"(Shitani yabakumiriye kugana inzira ya Allah) kugira ngo batubamira Allah, We ushyira ahagaragara ibyihishe mu birere no mu isi, ndetse azi ibyo muhisha n’ibyo mugaragaza"
  27,26,"Allah, nta yindi mana ibaho ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri itari We, Nyagasani wa Ar’shi ihambaye"